data.description: Indulge in the epitome of serene living with this meticulously renovated canal-front home and its charming separate bungalow. No detail has been overlooked in the comprehensive transformation undertaken over the past 2 years, ensuring a stress-free and luxurious lifestyle.  From the brand-new roof to the very foundation, every aspect of this home has been expertly addressed. Updates include a state-of-the-art A/C system, plumbing, electric wiring, windows, doors, appliances, water filtration, supports, seawall, landscaping, and a delightful spa. The separate bungalow adds an extra layer of versatility to the property.  Step into an open-concept kitchen seamlessly flowing into the spacious lanai, providing both privacy and an ideal setting for entertaining. The main house boasts 2 bedrooms and 2 baths, fully furnished with sheets, and the cabinets stocked with high-quality flatware, dishes, and cookware. The living room is designed for comfort, offering a perfect layout for entertaining or enjoying a show on the TV.  The fully screened lanai, adorned with oversized fans, ensures a continuous refreshing breeze, making it an ideal spot for relaxation. Take advantage of the swim spa, offering options for aquatic workouts, a refreshing dip, or a spa-like experience with bubbles and heat.  The efficiency bungalow comes complete with its own full bath, A/C, and a porch overlooking the canal. For water enthusiasts, the brand-new seawall with water and electric hookups awaits your vessel, provided you have a knack for reading the tides.  Landscaping with strategically placed lighting enhances the charm of this fully fenced property. Whether you're seeking a primary residence with no need for updates, a canal-side vacation retreat, or an income- generating property for rental or Airbnb, this home offers endless possibilities. No HOA restrictions add to the appeal. Inquire with your agent about additional attachments for more information. Envision the transformative impact this property could have on your lifestyle – a truly exceptional investment opportunity.
